  "text": "In this section, we focus on the adaptive transmission scheme and examine its secrecy performance in the MISO wiretap channel. First, we introduce the principle of the general adaptive scheme. Second, we derive closed-form expressions for the secrecy outage probability which is distinct from (14) and the secure transmission probability which is distinct from [CITATION_1] . Using these expressions, the EST, the probability of non-zero secrecy capacity, and the ε-outage secrecy capacity are obtained. To optimize the secrecy performance, we first determine the optimal power allocation ratio α † that minimizes the secrecy outage probability. Then we determine the joint optimal pair (α †• , R †• s ) that maximizes the EST.",
